#: ../../../reference/ufuncs.rst:410
msgid ""
"The bit-wise operators & and \\| are the proper way to perform element-by-"
"element array comparisons. Be sure you understand the operator precedence: "
"``(a > 2) & (a < 5)`` is the proper syntax because ``a > 2 & a < 5`` will "
"result in an error due to the fact that ``2 & a`` is evaluated first."
msgstr ""

